strings.Value: "Damnable kobolds! What a pleasure it would be to settle the score with Tartuk, that foul scaly bastard!"
"This Tartuk is rumored to be different from his kin... and I mean not only the color of his scales."
"Your hatred for kobolds is like mine for trolls. It's... understandable."
"Don't let personal quarrels cloud your judgment, Jubilost."
